  "texts": [
    "This not only addressed the problem of data scarcity but also solved the lowclass problem of the BUSI dataset.",
    "The similarity between the BreakHis and BUSI datasets also contributed to the success of the few-shot classification.",
    "To the best of our knowledge, this study is the first attempt to apply few-shot classification using meta-learning on the BUSI dataset.",
    "The methodology we used can be adapted to other datasets with similar problems.In the study, two meta-learning algorithms were used: metric-based prototypical networks (ProtoNet) and optimization-based first-order model agnostic meta-learning (FOMAML).",
    "The results of the experiments showed that ProtoNet outperformed FOMAML."
